window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The battle lines have been drawn.</b></p> <p>The peace in West Hollow was shattered the night Segovax attacked. Now wearing the body of the Duke of Midhaven, the rogue war wizard prepares to finish the job, unleashing his new army on our unsuspecting town.</p> <p>But we won’t go down without a fight. With my new ally Corinne and my trusted companions Lynnette and Serena, we’re going to find a way to stop Segovax once and for all.</p> <p><b>Even if it sparks a war that engulfs us all.</b></p>"; 
